videos.headline: Stave injured in Badgers' win
videos.description: Wisconsin QB Joel Stave leaves the game in the first quarter with a head injury, but Bart Houston fills in and throws for 232 yards, two touchdowns and two inceptions in a 24-13 win over Illinois.
